+config REALTEK_CR_PCI
+	tristate "Realtek PCI-E Card Reader Adapter Driver"
+	depends on PCI && REALTEK_CR_CORE
+	help
+	  Say Y here to include driver code to support the Realtek
+	  PCI-E card reader.
